    <title>BIOTEM 제품 목록</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .product-card { border: 1px solid #ddd; padding: 15px; margin: 10px; border-radius: 10px; display: inline-block; width: 250px; }
        .price { color: #e44d26; font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2em; }
        .buy-btn { background-color: #4CAF50; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>맞춤형 지주대 제품 목록</h1>
    
